HOW TO USE:
* In the shell, run "python bot.py <server[:port]> <channel> <bot nick> [if using link log: True]
* To use the link log, your last arg should be "True"
* To use Puppy Bot you need a Flickr API key.

REQUIREMENTS:
* python-requests
* python flickr
* python irc 
* flickr API key (store in secret_settings.py)
* empty text file to begin, called 'links_in_channel.txt'